               </spanGrp>
            </div>
            <div xml:id="T01_AD_F.67_Naameh_Maslaxbefore1_a17">
               <u xml:lang="ar-acm-x-shawi-vicav"
                  who="corpus:LEB_NAA_2023_AD_F.67_Speaker1"
                  xml:id="T01_AD_F.67_Naameh_Maslaxbefore1_a17_u1"
                  end="#T22"
                  start="#T21">
                  <gap reason="unconsented"/>
               </u>
               <spanGrp type="Translation">
                  <span xml:lang="en"
                        target="#T01_AD_F.67_Naameh_Maslaxbefore1_a17"
                        xml:id="a37">Yes. What can I tell you. Absolutely everything</span>
               </spanGrp>
            </div>
            <div xml:id="T01_AD_F.67_Naameh_Maslaxbefore1_a18">
               <u xml:lang="ar-acm-x-shawi-vicav"
                  who="corpus:LEB_NAA_2023_AD_F.67_Speaker1"
                  xml:id="T01_AD_F.67_Naameh_Maslaxbefore1_a18_u1"
                  end="#T23"
                  start="#T22">
                  <gap reason="unconsented"/>
               </u>
               <spanGrp type="Translation">
                  <span xml:lang="en"
                        target="#T01_AD_F.67_Naameh_Maslaxbefore1_a18"
                        xml:id="a38">Whatever you say about al-Maslakh (is) beautiful.</span>
               </spanGrp>
            </div>
            <div xml:id="T01_AD_F.67_Naameh_Maslaxbefore1_a19">
               <u xml:lang="ar-acm-x-shawi-vicav"
                  who="corpus:LEB_NAA_2023_AD_F.67_Speaker1"
                  xml:id="T01_AD_F.67_Naameh_Maslaxbefore1_a19_u1"
                  end="#T24"
                  start="#T23">
                  <gap reason="unconsented"/>
               </u>
               <spanGrp type="Translation">
                  <span xml:lang="en"
                        target="#T01_AD_F.67_Naameh_Maslaxbefore1_a19"
                        xml:id="a39">(I mean) there were no grudges among people.</span>
               </spanGrp>
            </div>
            <div xml:id="T01_AD_F.67_Naameh_Maslaxbefore1_a40">
               <u xml:lang="ar-acm-x-shawi-vicav"
                  who="corpus:LEB_NAA_2023_AD_F.67_Speaker1"
                  xml:id="T01_AD_F.67_Naameh_Maslaxbefore1_a40_u1"
                  end="#T25"
                  start="#T24">
                  <gap reason="unconsented"/>
               </u>
               <spanGrp type="Translation">
                  <span xml:lang="en"
                        target="#T01_AD_F.67_Naameh_Maslaxbefore1_a40"
                        xml:id="a42">When a foreigner would die there, they would take ... They would repatriate him to his country.</span>
               </spanGrp>
            </div>
            <div xml:id="T01_AD_F.67_Naameh_Maslaxbefore1_a41">
               <u xml:lang="ar-acm-x-shawi-vicav"
                  who="corpus:LEB_NAA_2023_AD_F.67_Speaker1"
                  xml:id="T01_AD_F.67_Naameh_Maslaxbefore1_a41_u1"
                  end="#T26"
                  start="#T25">
                  <gap reason="unconsented"/>
               </u>
               <spanGrp type="Translation">
                  <span xml:lang="en"
                        target="#T01_AD_F.67_Naameh_Maslaxbefore1_a41"
                        xml:id="a43">I mean everyone, whether stranger or close relative, (if) this is from Arab al-Maslakh, they don't differenciate.</span>
               </spanGrp>
            </div>
         </div>
      </body>
   </text>
